Introduction

Ryu Sarang is a South Korean dancer, singer, and rapper under WAKEONE.

In 2024, she was a contestant on Mnet' survival show I-LAND2: N/a, where she ended up ranking 5th place in the final with 319,693 votes, thus securing her spot as a member of the final group, izna.

Ryu Sarang made her debut with the group on November 25, 2024, with the release of their first mini album titled "N/a".
